studyArms.name: Veliparib + Carboplatin + Paclitaxel
studyArms.description: Veliparib 120 mg BID (Days -2 to 5) in combination with Carboplatin AUC 6 (Day 1) and Paclitaxel 80 mg/m2 (Days 1, 8, 15) on a 21-day cycle. Subjects who discontinue chemotherapy without progression continue Veliparib monotherapy with titration.
